@node "Future" "Future of DFB"

 Firstly, DFB is not perfect. As far as BBS file bases go it is getting
 there though! So what do I plan to do to DFB in the future?
 
 * Utilities, doors e.g.: Top Up/Downloaders, File list generator.
 * XPR transfer protocol libraries. This way DFB will support more protocols
   such as Super Zmodem, Bimodem etc...
 * Hopefully a file layout editor
 * Daily download limits
 * CDROM/DAT section support (including multiple dfb.data file support)
 * Lots of minor enhancements 
 * Can't think of anything else. All of the features I could think of are
   already in it!

@endnode

